msgid "0:ソファに座り、僕はぼんやりと、ＰＣの上に貼ってある星来たんポスターを眺めていた。[linebreak]部屋はすっかり片付いていた。[%p]"
msgstr "0:I sat down on the sofa, staring blankly at the Seira-tan poster on my wall. My room was much cleaner that it had been.[%p]"

msgid "100:僕がすべてを話した後、しばらく無言で怯えていた七海は、突然“部屋を片付けよう”って言い出したんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "100:After I'd finished my story, Nanami had sat there silently for a while, before suddenly saying that she wanted to clean my room.[%p]"

msgid "200:それで、２〜３時間かけてこの状態にまでした。[linebreak]きっと七海は、身体を動かしていればあれこれ考えなくて済むって考えたんだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "200:After two or three hours, it was in a much better state. Nanami had probably wanted to do something to take her mind off what I'd told her, I assumed.[%p]"

msgid "300:その七海は今、ベッドの上で横になっている。[%p]"
msgstr "300:Now she was lying on the bed.[%p]"

msgid "400:あのベッドが本来の用途として使われるのは、いつ以来だろう。[linebreak]このコンテナハウスで暮らすようになって最初の数ヶ月は、僕もちゃんと使っていたような気がする。[%p]"
msgstr "400:How long had it been since anybody had used that bed for its intended purpose? I vaguely remembered sleeping in it for the first few months after I moved here.[%p]"

msgid "500:部屋を片付けてるときは、すごく面倒くさくて、勘弁してくれよって思ってたけど、今にして思うと片付けたのは正解だったと思う。[%p]"
msgstr "500:I hadn't wanted her to clean my room, but now that it was done, I realized it was the right thing to do.[%p]"

msgid "600:昨晩は、七海がソファで、僕は床で寝た。[linebreak]寝心地は最悪だっただけに、今晩はソファで眠れるのが嬉しい。[%p]"
msgstr "600:Last night she'd slept on the sofa, and I'd slept on the floor. It had been horribly uncomfortable, and I was glad for the chance to be able to sleep on the sofa tonight.[%p]"

msgid "700:と言っても、普段の僕はいつも夜型の生活をしているから、七海と違ってこんな早い時間に寝ることなんてできない。[%p]"
msgstr "700:As nocturnal as I was, though, I couldn't go to sleep as early as Nanami.[%p]"

msgid "800:まあ、今はとっくに日付も変わっちゃってるけど、僕にとってはそれは“早い時間”なんだ。[linebreak]いつもは、空が白み始めてから寝てるからね。[%p]"
msgstr "800:Well, it was past midnight, so maybe it wasn't early. But even that was early for me. I always went to sleep around the time the sun started to come up.[%p]"

msgid "900:というわけでソファに座ったまま、こうしてぼんやりしている。[linebreak]七海はもう寝たのかな？　寝息は特に聞こえてこないけど。[%p]"
msgstr "900:So here I was, sitting on the sofa, just staring into space. Had Nanami gone to sleep? I couldn't hear the sound of her snoring.[%p]"

msgid "1000:と、そんな僕の考えが伝わったかのように、七海がもぞもぞと寝返りを打ち、顔を出した。[%p]"
msgstr "1000:Maybe she read my mind, because she turned over in the bed and poked her head out from the covers.[%p]"

msgid "1100:[name]七海[line]「ねえ、おにぃ」[%p]"
msgstr "1100:[name]七海[line]Hey, Brother.[%p]"

msgid "1200:[name]拓巳[line]「ね、寝てなかったの？」[%p]"
msgstr "1200:[name]拓巳[line]Y-You couldn't sleep?[%p]"

msgid "1300:[name]七海[line]「うん……」[%p]"
msgstr "1300:[name]七海[line]Yeah...[%p]"

msgid "1400:七海はなにかを言いたげな表情をしている。[linebreak]やがて、おずおずとつぶやいた。[%p]"
msgstr "1400:Nanami looked like she wanted to say something. After a few moments of hesitation, she whispered.[%p]"

msgid "1500:[name]七海[line]「あのね、一緒に、寝てあげよっか……？」[%p]"
msgstr "1500:[name]七海[line]Um, want to sleep in the bed?[%p]"

msgid "1600:[name]拓巳[line]「な……！？」[%p]"
msgstr "1600:[name]拓巳[line]What?[%p]"

msgid "1700:[name]七海[line]「あ、別に、ナナが一緒に寝たいわけじゃないよ？　ほらっ、ダメダメおにぃは、怖くて怖くて１人じゃ寝付けないみたいだから、ホントはイヤだけど、今日だけは特別、ってことで……」[%p]"
msgstr "1700:[name]七海[line]Oh, um. It's not like I want to sleep in the same bed as you, okay? But you know, you're such a loser and a scaredy-cat that you probably can't sleep on your own, so you know... just for today...[%p]"

msgid "1800:だんだん、言葉に勢いがなくなっていく。[linebreak]強がってはいるけど、結局のところ七海自身が怖くて眠れないらしい。[%p]"
msgstr "1800:Her words started to have more and more force behind them. She wasn't coming out and saying it, but from the sound of things, she was too scared to sleep.[%p]"

msgid "1900:というわけで、こんな状況になった……。[%p]"
msgstr "1900:And so now here we were.[%p]"

msgid "2000:[name]七海[line]「もし、いやらしいことしたら、本気で怒るからね……！」[%p]"
msgstr "2000:[name]七海[line]If you do anything naughty, I'll get really mad, okay?[%p]"

msgid "2100:[name]拓巳[line]「す、するわけないだろ……」[%p]"
msgstr "2100:[name]拓巳[line]O-Of course I won't.[%p]"

msgid "2200:[name]七海[line]「分かんないじゃん、ついムラムラしちゃったりするんじゃないの？」[%p]"
msgstr "2200:[name]七海[line]How can I be sure? You might get all excited or something.[%p]"

msgid "2300:[name]拓巳[line]「しないって、言ってるだろ……。い、妹に、ムラムラなんか、で、できるか」[%p]"
msgstr "2300:[name]拓巳[line]I w-won't. Y-You're my sister. I don't consider you cute.[%p]"

msgid "2400:[name]七海[line]「むぅ〜。それはそれでちょっとショック……。少しくらい、ムラムラしてほしいなぁ……」[%p]"
msgstr "2400:[name]七海[line]Hmph. That kind of hurts, in a way. You could at least find me a little cute.[%p]"

msgid "2500:[name]拓巳[line]「だ、誰がするか……。文句ばっかり言うなら、一緒に寝るのは、な、無しだ……」[%p]"
msgstr "2500:[name]拓巳[line]N-No way... If you keep complaining, I'll go sleep on the sofa.[%p]"

msgid "2600:[name]七海[line]「……ごめんなさい。もう言いません」[%p]"
msgstr "2600:[name]七海[line]I'm sorry. I won't say that again.[%p]"

msgid "2700:すねたように唇を尖らし、黙り込む。[%p]"
msgstr "2700:She pouted and fell silent.[%p]"

msgid "2800:[name]七海[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "2800:[name]七海[line]...[%p]"

msgid "2900:う、うーむ。これは、想像以上の恥ずかしさだ……。[linebreak]それに、妙にドキドキする……。[%p]"
msgstr "2900:H-Hmm... This was more embarrassing than I expected. And... my heart was pounding, too.[%p]"

msgid "3000:たとえ相手が妹とは言え、三次元の女子とここまで接近した状態で、しかも同じベッドで寝てるなんてシチュエーションは、経験したことがない。[%p]"
msgstr "3000:Even if she was my little sister, I'd never been this close to a 3D girl, let alone slept in the same bed as one.[%p]"

msgid "3100:口ではムラムラなんかしないって言ったけど、実はウソ……。正直言って、ムラムラしそうです……。[%p]"
msgstr "3100:I said I didn't think she was cute, but that was a lie. She actually kind of was.[%p]"

msgid "3200:しかも、なんで七海はこっちを見てるんだ。[linebreak]目を閉じろ。[linebreak]こっち見んな。[%p]"
msgstr "3200:And why was she looking at me, anyway? Close your eyes. Don't look at me.[%p]"

msgid "3300:[name]七海[line]「なんだか、変な感じだね……」[%p]"
msgstr "3300:[name]七海[line]T-This feels kind of weird.[%p]"

msgid "3400:[name]七海[line]「ねえ、おにぃは、ナナのこと、うっとうしいって、思ってる……？」[%p]"
msgstr "3400:[name]七海[line]Hey, Brother, do you think I'm annoying?[%p]"

msgid "3500:[name]拓巳[line]「え……」[%p]"
msgstr "3500:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?[%p]"

msgid "3600:[name]七海[line]「ふーん、思ってるんだ……」[%p]"
msgstr "3600:[name]七海[line]Hmm... You do, huh?[%p]"

msgid "3700:思ってる。生意気だし、いつも口うるさいし、なんだかんだ干渉してくるし。[linebreak]……思ってた、って言った方が正しいかな。[%p]"
msgstr "3700:I did. She was bratty. She talked back. And she wouldn't leave me alone. At least, that's what I used to think.[%p]"

msgid "3800:ここ２日間くらい、七海と一緒に過ごす時間が増えて。[%p]"
msgstr "3800:After spending more time with her in the past few days, I'd changed my mind.[%p]"

msgid "3900:しかも七海はすごく弱ってて、そのくせ情けない僕に笑顔で付き合ってくれた。[%p]"
msgstr "3900:She was in bad shape herself, and yet she was always there to smile at me when things were rough.[%p]"

msgid "4000:そのことを考えると、案外この妹の存在は僕にとって、とても救いになってるんじゃないかって、少し思えてきた。[%p]"
msgstr "4000:Maybe having a little sister wasn't so bad after all.[%p]"

msgid "4100:[name]拓巳[line]「思って、ないよ……」[%p]"
msgstr "4100:[name]拓巳[line]I don't...[%p]"

msgid "4200:[name]七海[line]「別に、思われたって平気だよ」[%p]"
msgstr "4200:[name]七海[line]It's okay if you do.[%p]"

msgid "4300:[name]七海[line]「ただね、勘違いしてほしくないんだけど……、ナナは、おにぃのこと、嫌いなわけじゃ、ないからね？」[%p]"
msgstr "4300:[name]七海[line]But... I just want you to know... that I don't hate you or anything.[%p]"

msgid "4400:い、いきなりなにを言い出すんだ、こいつは……？[%p]"
msgstr "4400:W-What was she talking about?[%p]"

msgid "4500:[name]七海[line]「おにぃって、前、入院してたでしょ？　それで――」[%p]"
msgstr "4500:[name]七海[line]You were in the hospital before, right? And then...[%p]"

msgid "4600:[name]拓巳[line]「に、入院は、してない。通院、してただけだ」[%p]"
msgstr "4600:[name]拓巳[line]I was never in the hospital. I'd been going to one, but never stayed there.[%p]"

msgid "4700:[name]七海[line]「うそ。入院してたじゃん」[%p]"
msgstr "4700:[name]七海[line]Liar. You were in the hospital for a long time.[%p]"

msgid "4800:[name]拓巳[line]「してない。お前の、勘違い」[%p]"
msgstr "4800:[name]拓巳[line]I wasn't. You're mistaken.[%p]"

msgid "4900:[name]七海[line]「そうだっけ……？」[%p]"
msgstr "4900:[name]七海[line]Am I?[%p]"

msgid "5000:[name]七海[line]「まあいいけど、とにかくおにぃが学校も行けなくて大変だったときに、ナナがしっかりしなくちゃって、思うようになったの」[%p]"
msgstr "5000:[name]七海[line]Well, whatever. Anyway, when you couldn't go to school, I started to think that I had to be the big sister now.[%p]"

msgid "5100:[name]七海[line]「いつもおにぃに口うるさくあれこれ言ってたのだって……、そういう理由なんだよ？」[%p]"
msgstr "5100:[name]七海[line]That's why I was always so bossy with you, understand?[%p]"

msgid "5200:[name]七海[line]「おにぃが、嫌いだったからとかじゃ、ないよ？」[%p]"
msgstr "5200:[name]七海[line]Not because I don't like you.[%p]"

msgid "5300:[name]七海[line]「昔は……おにぃが病院に行くようになる前は、ナナはいつもおにぃに甘えてたよね」[%p]"
msgstr "5300:[name]七海[line]A long time ago... before you started going to the hospital... I always let you spoil me.[%p]"

msgid "5400:[name]七海[line]「おにぃは、ナナにとっては頼りになるおにぃだった」[%p]"
msgstr "5400:[name]七海[line]You were my big brother, and I went to you for everything.[%p]"

msgid "5500:[name]七海[line]「おにぃのこと、大好きだった」[%p]"
msgstr "5500:[name]七海[line]I loved you.[%p]"

msgid "5600:か、過去形かよ……。[%p]"
msgstr "5600:D-Did you have to say it in past tense?[%p]"

msgid "5700:[name]七海[line]「だから、今度はナナがしっかりして、少しでもおにぃの負担にならないようにして、おにぃの役に立とうと思って……」[%p]"
msgstr "5700:[name]七海[line]So now I'm trying to be the big sister, to help you as much as I can.[%p]"

msgid "5800:[name]七海[line]「あんまり、役に立ててたかどうか、分かんないけど……、えへへ……」[%p]"
msgstr "5800:[name]七海[line]I don't know if I'm really helping, though... Ehehe.[%p]"

msgid "5900:[name]拓巳[line]「……ダメな、兄貴で、ごめん」[%p]"
msgstr "5900:[name]拓巳[line]I'm sorry I'm such a loser.[%p]"

msgid "6000:こんな状況だからか、普段はとても言えないようなことも、素直に口にできた。[%p]"
msgstr "6000:Maybe because of everything that was going on, I found myself able to say things that I'd never be able to say otherwise.[%p]"

msgid "6100:[name]七海[line]「気にしないでいいよ。兄妹だもん。それにナナは、昔の、頼りがいのあるおにぃのことも知ってるし」[%p]"
msgstr "6100:[name]七海[line]Don't worry about it. We're brother and sister. And I know how you used to be, back when you weren't like this.[%p]"

msgid "6200:[name]七海[line]「どんなにダメでも、ナナは、おにぃのこと、嫌いになんてならないからね？」[%p]"
msgstr "6200:[name]七海[line]So, no matter how big a loser you are, I'll never hate you, okay?[%p]"

msgid "6300:[name]拓巳[line]「うう、七海……」[%p]"
msgstr "6300:[name]拓巳[line]Wah... Nanami...[%p]"

msgid "6400:七海が、こんな風に思っててくれたなんて……。[%p]"
msgstr "6400:I had no idea that she felt that way.[%p]"

msgid "6500:すごく嬉しい。三次元の妹なんてイラネ、って思ってた自分が許せない。[linebreak]七海がいてくれてよかった。[%p]"
msgstr "6500:It made me so incredibly happy. I couldn't believe that I'd ever hated having a 3D sister. I was so glad she was here.[%p]"

msgid "6600:[name]七海[line]「でも、今日は……ちょっとだけ、甘えても、いい……？」[%p]"
msgstr "6600:[name]七海[line]But... today, can you be there for me?[%p]"

msgid "6700:[name]七海[line]「さっきは、強がり言っちゃったけど、ホントはね……」[%p]"
msgstr "6700:[name]七海[line]I was trying to act big and tough back there, but the truth is...[%p]"

msgid "6800:[name]七海[line]「１人で、横になってると……どんどん、怖い想像ばっかり、しちゃうんだ……」[%p]"
msgstr "6800:[name]七海[line]When I'm lying here alone, I start to think about all kinds of scary things.[%p]"

msgid "6900:[name]七海[line]「だから、おにぃに、甘えたかったの。安心したかったの……」[%p]"
msgstr "6900:[name]七海[line]So, I wanted you to be next to me. I wanted to feel safer.[%p]"

msgid "7000:身体を丸めて、七海は僕の胸に頭を埋めてきた。[linebreak]七海からは、いい匂いがした。[%p]"
msgstr "7000:She curled up and put her head against my chest. Nanami smelled good.[%p]"

msgid "7100:[name]七海[line]「ずっと、こうしたかったんだ……」[%p]"
msgstr "7100:[name]七海[line]I always wanted to do this.[%p]"

msgid "7200:[name]七海[line]「ずっと、おにぃに、甘えたかったんだ……」[%p]"
msgstr "7200:[name]七海[line]I always wanted you to be there for me.[%p]"

msgid "7300:たまらず、七海のほっそりした身体を抱きしめていた。[linebreak]きつく。きつく。[%p]"
msgstr "7300:I wrapped my arms around her slender body. Tightly... So tightly.[%p]"

msgid "7400:七海さえいてくれれば、他はなにもいらない。[%p]"
msgstr "7400:As long as she was here, I didn't need anything else.[%p]"

msgid "7500:星来たんフィギュアも、エンスーでの尊敬も、必要ない。[linebreak]この、血の通った、僕のことをこんなにも思っててくれる七海さえいてくれればいい。[%p]"
msgstr "7500:Not my Seira-tan figures, not my ESO rep. None of that. All I needed was my living, flesh-and-blood sister, who cared about me so much.[%p]"

msgid "7600:七海の温もりを肌で感じることで、僕は安心できた。[linebreak]そして気が付けば、心地いい眠りに落ちていた――[%p]"
msgstr "7600:Feeling the warmth of her skin made me feel so much better. The next thing I knew, I'd fallen into a pleasant sleep.[%p]"

